Sentencas: A dimples array structure at mesoscale is fabricated on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte substrate by spraying deposition.
Titulo: A novel method of modifying electrolyte surface at mesoscale for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Microstructure and morphology of the mesoscale dimples configuration are investigated via scanning electron microscopy and the results show that the uniform dimples structure is obtained by spray deposition.
Titulo: A novel method of modifying electrolyte surface at mesoscale for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With the dimples structure on electrolyte surface, the power density of the electrolyte-supported fuel cell is increased by a factor of 2.
Titulo: A novel method of modifying electrolyte surface at mesoscale for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) measurements further reveal that the dimples structure reduces the polarization resistance of the cell, resulting in the improvement of cell performance.
Titulo: A novel method of modifying electrolyte surface at mesoscale for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
